---
title: Smart Mexican-Inspired Albondigas Soup with Rice-Stuffed Chicken Meatballs and Cilantro
description: Chicken meatballs rolled with rice and fresh herbs are a game changer in this hearty yet light soup! Chipotle sauce lends a delicate heat and smokiness to our take on albondigas soup. Packed with veggies, this soup is just what you need on a chilly night.

